description: Including sayings from Gandhi, Martin Luther King, Aristotle, and a wide variety of other famous public figures, wise guy has a saying that will give you some insight regardless of which one you receive.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask wise guy to tell me a saying
Alexa, tell wise guy to give me a saying
Alexa, open wise guy and tell me a wise saying
name: WiseGuy
shortDescription: Brighten your day with insightful sayings. Ask a wise guy to tell one whenever you want.
